---
// src/pages/civil/cee335l/index.astro
const title = "CEE335L — Reinforced Concrete Design Lab";
const description = "Learn structural analysis using ETABS. Covers RC building frames, bridge portals, BNBC wind & seismic loads, and AASHTO bridge codes. Interactive intuition-first course guide.";
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>{title} | Mathify</title>
  <meta name="description" content={description} />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Mono:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400&family=Playfair+Display:wght@700;900&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />

  <!-- KaTeX -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.9/dist/katex.min.css" />
  <script defer src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.9/dist/katex.min.js"></script>
  <script defer src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.9/dist/contrib/auto-render.min.js"
    onload="renderMathInElement(document.body,{delimiters:[{left:'\\(',right:'\\)',display:false},{left:'\\[',right:'\\]',display:true}]})"></script>

  <style>
    :root {
      --bg:        #0d0d0f;
      --bg2:       #13131a;
      --bg3:       #1a1a24;
      --border:    #2a2a3a;
      --text:      #e8e8f0;
      --muted:     #7a7a9a;
      --accent:    #f0a500;
      --accent2:   #3ecfcf;
      --accent3:   #e05c5c;
      --green:     #4ade80;
      --mono:      'Space Mono', monospace;
      --serif:     'Playfair Display', serif;
      --sans:      'Inter', sans-serif;
    }

    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      font-family: var(--sans);
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    /* ── NAV ── */
    nav {
      position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100;
      background: rgba(13,13,15,0.92);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 2rem;
    }
    .nav-logo { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 1rem; color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; }
    .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 1.5rem; list-style: none; }
    .nav-links a { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--muted); text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 0.05em; transition: color 0.2s; }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--text); }
    .breadcrumb { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--muted); margin-left: auto; letter-spacing: 0.08em; }
    .breadcrumb a { color: var(--muted); text-decoration: none; }
    .breadcrumb a:hover { color: var(--accent); }

    /* ── HERO ── */
    .hero {
      padding: 5rem 2rem 3rem;
      max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .hero-tag {
      font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.7rem;
      color: var(--accent); letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 1rem;
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
    }
    .hero-tag::before { content: ''; width: 2rem; height: 1px; background: var(--accent); }
    .hero h1 {
      font-family: var(--serif); font-size: clamp(2rem,5vw,3.5rem);
      font-weight: 900; line-height: 1.1;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .hero h1 span { color: var(--accent); }
    .hero-sub {
      font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--muted); max-width: 600px;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    .hero-meta {
      display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.75rem; margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }
    .badge {
      font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      padding: 0.3rem 0.75rem; border-radius: 4px; border: 1px solid;
    }
    .badge-amber  { color: var(--accent);  border-color: var(--accent);  background: rgba(240,165,0,0.08); }
    .badge-teal   { color: var(--accent2); border-color: var(--accent2); background: rgba(62,207,207,0.08); }
    .badge-red    { color: var(--accent3); border-color: var(--accent3); background: rgba(224,92,92,0.08); }
    .badge-green  { color: var(--green);   border-color: var(--green);   background: rgba(74,222,128,0.08); }
    .badge-muted  { color: var(--muted);   border-color: var(--border);  background: var(--bg2); }

    .hero-stats {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit,minmax(120px,1fr));
      gap: 1rem; margin-top: 2rem;
    }
    .stat-box {
      background: var(--bg2); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 8px; padding: 1rem; text-align: center;
    }
    .stat-num { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 1.8rem; color: var(--accent); display: block; }
    .stat-label { font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--muted); letter-spacing: 0.05em; }

    /* ── SECTION LAYOUT ── */
    .section { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 4rem 2rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
    .section:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

    .section-num {
      font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.65rem; color: var(--accent);
      letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase;
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }
    .section-num::after { content: ''; flex: 0 0 3rem; height: 1px; background: var(--border); }

    .section h2 {
      font-family: var(--serif); font-size: clamp(1.5rem,3vw,2.2rem);
      font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .section-intro { color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 2.5rem; max-width: 620px; }

    /* ── VIEW CARDS (Civil / Physics / Math / Core) ── */
    .view-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    @media(max-width:600px) { .view-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

    .view-card {
      background: var(--bg2); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 10px; padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
      transition: border-color 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
    }
    .view-card:hover { border-color: var(--accent); transform: translateY(-2px); }
    .view-label {
      font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .view-card.civil  .view-label { color: var(--accent2); }
    .view-card.physics .view-label { color: var(--accent); }
    .view-card.math    .view-label { color: var(--accent3); }
    .view-card.core {
      grid-column: 1 / -1;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(240,165,0,0.06), rgba(62,207,207,0.06));
      border-color: rgba(240,165,0,0.3);
    }
    .view-card.core .view-label { color: var(--green); }
    .view-card h4 { font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .view-card p  { font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--muted); }

    /* ── INTERACTIVE: LOAD VISUALIZER ── */
    #load-canvas-wrapper {
      background: var(--bg2); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .load-controls {
      display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.5rem;
      padding: 1rem 1.25rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .load-btn {
      font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      padding: 0.35rem 0.85rem; border-radius: 6px; border: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: var(--bg3); color: var(--muted); cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.2s;
    }
    .load-btn.active { color: var(--bg); border-color: transparent; }
    .load-btn[data-load="dead"].active   { background: #60a5fa; }
    .load-btn[data-load="live"].active   { background: var(--green); }
    .load-btn[data-load="wind"].active   { background: var(--accent2); }
    .load-btn[data-load="seismic"].active { background: var(--accent3); }
    #load-canvas { display: block; width: 100%; height: 320px; }
    .load-info {
      padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
      font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--muted);
      min-height: 70px;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .load-info strong { color: var(--text); }

    /* ── INTERACTIVE: ETABS PIPELINE ── */
    .pipeline {
      display: flex; gap: 0; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      overflow-x: auto; padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .pipe-step {
      flex: 0 0 auto; min-width: 130px;
      background: var(--bg2); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-right: none; padding: 1rem; cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.2s; position: relative;
    }
    .pipe-step:first-child { border-radius: 8px 0 0 8px; }
    .pipe-step:last-child  { border-right: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0; }
    .pipe-step.active { background: rgba(240,165,0,0.1); border-color: var(--accent); }
    .pipe-step::after {
      content: '›';
      position: absolute; right: -12px; top: 50%; transform: translateY(-50%);
      color: var(--border); font-size: 1.2rem; z-index: 1;
    }
    .pipe-step:last-child::after { display: none; }
    .pipe-num { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.65rem; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 0.3rem; }
    .pipe-label { font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 600; }
    .pipe-sub   { font-size: 0.68rem; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 0.2rem; }
    .pipe-detail {
      background: var(--bg2); border: 1px solid var(--accent);
      border-radius: 10px; padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem; display: none;
    }
    .pipe-detail.visible { display: block; animation: fadeIn 0.25s ease; }
    .pipe-detail h4 { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .pipe-detail ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; }
    .pipe-detail li {
      font-size: 0.85rem; padding: 0.3rem 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      color: var(--muted); display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.5rem;
    }
    .pipe-detail li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .pipe-detail li::before { content: '→'; color: var(--accent); flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 0.05rem; }

    /* ── INTERACTIVE: CODE EXPLORER ── */
    .code-tabs { display: flex; gap: 0; margin-bottom: 0; border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0; overflow: hidden; }
    .code-tab {
      flex: 1; padding: 0.75rem 1rem; cursor: pointer; text-align: center;
      font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.75rem; letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      background: var(--bg2); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-bottom: none; color: var(--muted); transition: all 0.2s;
    }
    .code-tab:not(:first-child) { border-left: none; }
    .code-tab.active { color: var(--bg); background: var(--accent); border-color: var(--accent); }
    .code-tab[data-code="aci"].active   { background: var(--accent2); border-color: var(--accent2); }
    .code-tab[data-code="aashto"].active { background: var(--accent3); border-color: var(--accent3); }
    .code-panel {
      background: var(--bg2); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px; padding: 1.5rem;
      display: none;
    }
    .code-panel.visible { display: block; animation: fadeIn 0.2s ease; }
    .code-panel h4 { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .code-panel .code-use { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .code-items { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 0.75rem; }
    @media(max-width:500px) { .code-items { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
    .code-item {
      background: var(--bg3); border-radius: 6px; padding: 0.75rem;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
    }
    .code-item-label { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.65rem; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
    .code-item-val   { font-weight: 600; }

    /* ── INTERACTIVE: DAY TIMELINE ── */
    .timeline { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0; }
    .day-row {
      display: flex; align-items: stretch; gap: 0;
      cursor: pointer; transition: background 0.15s;
      border-radius: 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .day-row:first-child { border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0; }
    .day-row:last-child  { border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
    .day-row:hover .day-main { background: var(--bg3); }
    .day-marker {
      flex: 0 0 56px;
      display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      background: var(--bg2); border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 1rem 0.5rem; gap: 0.25rem;
    }
    .day-marker.exam { background: rgba(224,92,92,0.1); }
    .day-num { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.65rem; color: var(--accent); }
    .day-icon { font-size: 1.1rem; }
    .day-main {
      flex: 1; background: var(--bg2); padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
      transition: background 0.15s;
    }
    .day-main.exam-main { background: rgba(224,92,92,0.04); }
    .day-title { font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.9rem; }
    .day-topics { font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 0.2rem; }
    .day-chevron { color: var(--border); transition: transform 0.2s, color 0.2s; font-size: 1rem; }
    .day-row.open .day-chevron { transform: rotate(90deg); color: var(--accent); }
    .day-expand {
      background: var(--bg3); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 1rem 1.25rem 1rem calc(56px + 1.25rem);
      display: none; font-size: 0.83rem;
    }
    .day-expand.visible { display: block; animation: slideDown 0.2s ease; }
    .day-expand ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.3rem; }
    .day-expand li { color: var(--muted); display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; align-items: flex-start; }
    .day-expand li::before { content: '›'; color: var(--accent2); flex-shrink: 0; }
    .day-expand .tip {
      margin-top: 0.75rem; padding: 0.6rem 0.9rem;
      background: rgba(62,207,207,0.06); border-left: 2px solid var(--accent2);
      border-radius: 0 6px 6px 0; color: var(--text); font-size: 0.82rem;
    }
    .exam-badge {
      font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.65rem; padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem;
      background: rgba(224,92,92,0.15); color: var(--accent3);
      border: 1px solid var(--accent3); border-radius: 4px;
    }

    /* ── INTERACTIVE: GRADE DONUT ── */
    .grade-wrapper {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: 200px 1fr; gap: 2rem; align-items: center;
    }
    @media(max-width:550px) { .grade-wrapper { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
    #gradeCanvas { display: block; }
    .grade-legend { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem; }
    .legend-item {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem; cursor: pointer;
      padding: 0.6rem 0.9rem; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: var(--bg2); transition: border-color 0.2s, transform 0.15s;
    }
    .legend-item:hover { border-color: var(--accent); transform: translateX(3px); }
    .legend-swatch { width: 12px; height: 12px; border-radius: 3px; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .legend-text { flex: 1; }
    .legend-name  { font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 600; }
    .legend-sub   { font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--muted); }
    .legend-pct   { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 1rem; color: var(--accent); }

    /* ── CTA ── */
    .cta-section {
      text-align: center; padding: 4rem 2rem;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .cta-section h2 { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
    .cta-section p  { color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    .btn-primary {
      display: inline-block; font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.8rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase;
      padding: 0.9rem 2rem; background: var(--accent); color: var(--bg);
      border-radius: 6px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 700;
      transition: opacity 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
    }
    .btn-primary:hover { opacity: 0.9; transform: translateY(-2px); }
    .btn-secondary {
      display: inline-block; font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.8rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase;
      padding: 0.9rem 2rem; background: transparent; color: var(--muted);
      border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 6px; text-decoration: none;
      margin-left: 1rem; transition: color 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
    }
    .btn-secondary:hover { color: var(--text); border-color: var(--muted); }

    /* ── FOOTER ── */
    footer {
      text-align: center; padding: 2rem;
      font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--muted);
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    footer a { color: var(--muted); text-decoration: none; }
    footer a:hover { color: var(--accent); }

    /* ── UTILS ── */
    @keyframes fadeIn    { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(6px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }
    @keyframes slideDown { from { opacity: 0; max-height: 0; } to { opacity: 1; max-height: 300px; } }

    .mono { font-family: var(--mono); }
    .accent { color: var(--accent); }
    .teal   { color: var(--accent2); }
    .red    { color: var(--accent3); }
    .green  { color: var(--green); }
    .muted  { color: var(--muted); }

    /* scrollbar */
    ::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 6px; height: 6px; }
    ::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: var(--bg); }
    ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: var(--border); border-radius: 3px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ── NAV ── -->
<nav>
  <a href="/" class="nav-logo">mathify</a>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="/math">Math</a></li>
    <li><a href="/physics">Physics</a></li>
    <li><a href="/civil">Civil</a></li>
    <li><a href="/ssc">SSC</a></li>
  </ul>
  <span class="breadcrumb">
    <a href="/civil.html">Civil</a> › CEE335L
  </span>
</nav>

<!-- ── HERO ── -->
<header class="hero">
  <div class="hero-tag">CEE — Senior Year · 4th Year · 1 Credit</div>
  <h1>Reinforced Concrete<br><span>Design Lab</span></h1>
  <p class="hero-sub">
    Learn to model, analyze, and design real RC structures using industry-standard ETABS software.
    Buildings, bridges, seismic loads — all grounded in BNBC, ACI, and AASHTO codes.
  </p>
  <div class="hero-meta">
    <span class="badge badge-amber">CEE335L</span>
    <span class="badge badge-teal">ETABS</span>
    <span class="badge badge-amber">BNBC</span>
    <span class="badge badge-teal">ACI</span>
    <span class="badge badge-red">AASHTO</span>
    <span class="badge badge-muted">Prereq: CEE335</span>
    <span class="badge badge-muted">Instructor: THK</span>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-stats">
    <div class="stat-box">
      <span class="stat-num">11</span>
      <span class="stat-label">Class Days</span>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-box">
      <span class="stat-num">3</span>
      <span class="stat-label">Design Codes</span>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-box">
      <span class="stat-num">2</span>
      <span class="stat-label">Structure Types</span>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-box">
      <span class="stat-num">1</span>
      <span class="stat-label">Software: ETABS</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>


<!-- ── SECTION 01: WHY ── -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="section-num">01 — Why this lab</div>
  <h2>Why does structural software matter?</h2>
  <p class="section-intro">
    Hand calculations get you through exams. Software gets you through real projects.
    Click each load type below to see what it actually does to a building.
  </p>

  <!-- VIEW CARDS -->
  <div class="view-grid">
    <div class="view-card civil">
      <div class="view-label">Civil View</div>
      <h4>The gap between textbooks and sites</h4>
      <p>Real buildings have irregular geometry, multiple load combinations, and 3D effects that make hand calculations impractical. ETABS handles all of this in minutes — engineers run dozens of load combos before choosing a design.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="view-card physics">
      <div class="view-label">Physics View</div>
      <h4>Forces come from many directions</h4>
      <p>Gravity pulls down (dead + live loads). Wind pushes sideways. Earthquakes shake the base. A structure must resist all of these — simultaneously — without yielding, buckling, or excessive drift. Visualize these below.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="view-card math">
      <div class="view-label">Math View</div>
      <h4>Linear superposition in action</h4>
      <p>ETABS applies the principle \(U = 1.2D + 1.6L + 0.5W\) (and many other combos per ACI/BNBC). The factored load envelope governs design at every section of every member simultaneously.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="view-card core">
      <div class="view-label">Core Idea</div>
      <h4>One model, infinite combinations</h4>
      <p>You build the geometry once. Then ETABS applies every load combination the code requires and finds the worst case at every point. That's impossible by hand for a real building — and exactly why this lab exists.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- LOAD VISUALIZER -->
  <div id="load-canvas-wrapper">
    <div class="load-controls">
      <span style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:0.7rem;color:var(--muted);margin-right:0.5rem;align-self:center;">LOAD TYPE →</span>
